{
  "stem": "22237.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know, they learned-- it was the trade you had to learn in anticipation of getting into another country, because nobody spoke the language.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Very few people spoke the language of whatever country you intended to go to.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was on our mind, just getting out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'm talking now about 1937.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "By that time, everybody wanted to get out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Were you still able to attend synagogue at that point?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To attend?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Synagogue we always attended.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, we always attended synagogue, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We would go to the synagogue, even if it was a little hard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sometimes going out, they would call us Jew, you know, this dirty Jew, we got so used to it that we hardly heard it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Hey, dirty Jew, you're going to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, we heard that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But yes, we always attended synagogue.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was-- became more important, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You were hoping that God will help you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, actually, next came-- in 1938, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was-- times were bad.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had heard of many incidents-- people being arrested, and for no reason.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Jews getting hurt in one way or another.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in 1938, we had the experience on October 28.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were five of us in the house, my parents and, as I mentioned before, and the three-- and my sister, brother, and myself.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that day, on October 28 at 5 o'clock in the morning, five SS men knocked on the door very heavily, pushed open the door, and came in and shouted, get dressed.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're-- you're being deported.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just get out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't even say you're being deported.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Get dressed and get out of here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember my parents, what is-- what for?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
